Interface WebsocketMetaChannel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable, WebsocketChannel, ch.colabproject.colab.generator.model.interfaces.WithJsonDiscriminator
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface WebsocketMetaChannel
extends WebsocketChannel
    A channel that can not be used as-is. It represent a conceptual channel. It should be resolved to a set of WebsocketEffectiveChannel.
